Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.73,0:00:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這片寂靜撕裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.14,0:00:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引領整個世界\N來到熾熱之焰的最深處吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.45,0:00:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的誓言\N灌注在朝天高舉的憤怒之拳中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.73,0:00:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再度點燃你的熱情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.63,0:00:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解放那沸騰不已的火紅熱血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.74,0:00:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰都已無法阻止你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.35,0:00:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓一片黑暗的明天\N燃起希望的光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.99,0:01:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化作捍衛弱者的獠牙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.66,0:01:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽超重爆炎霸!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.96,0:01:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫無畏懼的向前奔馳吧\N直到衝過那深紅色的終點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.87,0:01:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最後一刻燃盡一切吧\N超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.33,0:01:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能源波出力上升中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.97,0:01:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力巨星艦內\N開始出現局部區域重力異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.24,0:01:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去\N防護罩會完蛋的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.81,0:01:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朵莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.81,0:01:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再繼續把出力提高!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.61,0:01:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續把出力提高的話\N重力子能源會有失控危險的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.98,0:01:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.42,0:02:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擋住敵方能源波才是最優先事項
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.08,0:02:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解出力提升!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.02,0:02:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼斗牙英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.96,0:02:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們快點啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.17,0:02:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒這傢伙的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.11,0:02:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球就不會被\N大量殺戮機繼續襲擊了對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.15,0:02:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就把這當作最後一戰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.72,0:02:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於到大結局了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.39,0:02:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...提起幹勁來拼了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.79,0:02:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.03,0:02:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有來自重力巨星的通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.70,0:02:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛著神機Σ超重神闖進來了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.26,0:02:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.53,0:02:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說爸爸他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.74,0:03:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「魂之凱歌」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.71,0:03:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神加油啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.45,0:03:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定要平安回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.69,0:03:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候我們還要再一起出去玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.22,0:03:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...\N你絕對絕對要活著回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.53,0:03:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,井上小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.90,0:03:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重騎警的情形如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全機皆受到重創
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過生命反應都沒有出現異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.87,0:03:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.71,0:03:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛妳已經表現的很好了\N妳已經完成自己的任務了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.18,0:03:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.45,0:03:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.92,0:03:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們請你們救救人類...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請救救這地球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.56,0:03:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你們一定要平安無事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長振作點嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.60,0:03:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛力克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.47,0:04:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛隊長現在的那張臉\N一點都不像妳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.61,0:04:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們幾個啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.74,0:04:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是對平常充滿霸氣的隊長\N相當著迷喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.38,0:04:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個! 不准對上司無禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對對就是這個表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.35,0:04:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長還是要這樣才對嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.75,0:04:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雙超重神鐵定會得勝的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.29,0:04:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就相信桑德曼先生\N和他們的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.03,0:04:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.27,0:04:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺還真是游刃有餘呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.90,0:04:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸...請您保祐我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.94,0:04:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒耐性再和它耗下去了\N斗牙! 我們快點幹掉它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.95,0:04:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了\N要動手了各位!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.78,0:04:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.26,0:04:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.19,0:04:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.86,0:04:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爆炎霸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉它了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.88,0:05:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.31,0:05:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.41,0:05:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會...一點效果都沒有!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.78,0:05:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼強...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在才要開始來真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.69,0:05:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是再不快點的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.99,0:05:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼就會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.77,0:05:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類是種受污染的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.33,0:05:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一刻我就要為這些充滿\N慾望與鬥爭的歷史劃上休止符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.27,0:05:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.61,0:05:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的心已經被\N大量殺戮機系統污染了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.68,0:05:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類並不像你想像中的那樣污穢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.72,0:06:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有露菲拉擬似人格的人造人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.56,0:06:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會把她留在身邊的你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.33,0:06:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.50,0:06:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不正是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.57,0:06:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒有失去人類靈魂的證據嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.47,0:06:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.58,0:06:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准叫我妹妹的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.01,0:06:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此愛著我妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.18,0:06:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾經如此深愛著露菲拉的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你早就應該...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.35,0:06:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在她病入膏肓之前\N就注意到她已經生病了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.26,0:06:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把露菲拉害死的人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.59,0:06:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.03,0:06:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.48,0:07:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要上了喔愛娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的琉菜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.92,0:07:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽...超重...旋腕擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.94,0:07:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.98,0:07:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道真的沒有嗎?\N沒有能一口氣幹掉它的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.49,0:07:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...讓我去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.93,0:07:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大量殺戮機...只要感測到我\N系統就會停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀舅舅他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.77,0:07:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了要保護我\N所以才加入這個指令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.31,0:08:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要看到我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.21,0:08:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那台大量殺戮機\N就有可能會停止運作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.61,0:08:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說傻話了\N怎麼能讓妳去冒這個險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.85,0:08:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是程式已經被改寫的話\N那妳該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.96,0:08:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要舅舅他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.36,0:08:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還保有一絲關心我的感情的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.09,0:08:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,程式就應該還是原來那樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.46,0:08:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...想相信我的舅舅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.53,0:08:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管他到底變成什麼樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.60,0:08:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想相信舅舅...\N他的心一定還存在著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.91,0:08:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您不能去啊莉露小姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.38,0:08:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.58,0:08:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回來莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.86,0:08:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.83,0:08:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行無法讓它停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回來啊莉露!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.06,0:08:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露! 莉露小姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.26,0:08:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險! 快回駕駛艙去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.31,0:09:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀舅舅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.81,0:09:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.29,0:09:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙趁現在!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.09,0:09:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.33,0:09:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.76,0:09:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學風暴!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.68,0:09:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在豪魔內部\N確認發生了大爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.82,0:09:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方能源波正開始消退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.59,0:09:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.69,0:09:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.46,0:10:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.34,0:10:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.38,0:10:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.71,0:10:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會因為那個救莉露的程式\N而要了我的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.85,0:10:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然你還是保留了人性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.92,0:10:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你再怎麼否定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.16,0:10:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你仍然是人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荒謬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.60,0:10:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.20,0:10:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就讓這個豪魔\N直接去衝撞那顆行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.97,0:10:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要消滅上面的所有生命\N這樣應該就綽綽有餘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.57,0:10:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你休想!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.48,0:10:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你繼續礙事的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.22,0:11:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來為我們之間的宿命\N做個了斷的時刻終於到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.83,0:11:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就去陪露菲拉吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.50,0:11:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.10,0:11:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以死贖罪吧疾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.88,0:11:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.64,0:11:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露菲拉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快住手哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.01,0:11:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您不要傷害他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.78,0:11:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拷貝而來的露菲拉記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.46,0:11:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然擁有了自我意識嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.53,0:11:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只是在與你共渡的\N漫長時光中...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.76,0:11:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經寄宿了人類的魂魄而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.24,0:11:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連拷貝的妳\N也還是選擇了疾克嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.72,0:12:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我看看你這小子\N到底還能有什麼本事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.69,0:12:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.82,0:12:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.84,0:12:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了不起疾克...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.11,0:12:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀大哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.82,0:12:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是?大哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.86,0:12:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克原來是這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.53,0:12:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為大量殺戮機停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也自思考控制中\N解脫了嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.91,0:12:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀大哥...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.08,0:13:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許我一直...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.21,0:13:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都在等待著像這樣\N再度取回人心的時刻吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.19,0:13:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.46,0:13:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.73,0:13:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.10,0:13:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修紀大哥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.14,0:13:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都結束了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.99,0:13:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.99,0:13:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.49,0:13:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已經脫離了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.23,0:13:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快點回話啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.26,0:13:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.60,0:13:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.26,0:13:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉...我們得道別了莉露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.14,0:14:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.87,0:14:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我剩下要做的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.31,0:14:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只有為自己的罪付出代價...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.11,0:14:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您在說什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.41,0:14:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸您已經付出夠多了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.75,0:14:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算拋棄我們城裡的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.69,0:14:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是桑德曼先生不在的話\N那我們該怎麼辦呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.46,0:14:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼不論是城裡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.43,0:14:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是飛!\N大家都在等著你回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.70,0:14:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不可能沒有你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.70,0:14:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.60,0:14:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從好幾千年起\N就一直在等待著這一刻...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.54,0:14:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待這個變回人類的時刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.34,0:14:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待這個被安逸感籠罩的時刻...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.88,0:14:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.28,0:14:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔那多斯(死神)在呼喚我了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.48,0:14:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就...讓我安眠吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.89,0:14:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.05,0:14:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.06,0:14:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你少給我胡鬧了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.63,0:14:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.33,0:15:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然想獨自解脫\N簡直要把我給氣炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.73,0:15:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有一大堆帳還沒跟你算呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.70,0:15:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是被硬逼著\N來當超重神的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.31,0:15:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是吃了一大堆苦頭的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.71,0:15:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連綾香的下落都還沒問到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.04,0:15:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你居然想自己\N這樣隨隨便便的逃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.58,0:15:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別以為我會讓你這麼做!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.98,0:15:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有好多事情\N想要你告訴我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.58,0:15:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們一起回去吧\N桑德曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.02,0:15:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才能和您相認...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.79,0:15:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不要和您分開了爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.56,0:15:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香妳聽到了沒有?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.00,0:15:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點阻止桑德曼啊綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.33,0:15:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠阻止他的就只有妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.30,0:15:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香?她在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.29,0:16:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.56,0:16:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香...姊姊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.03,0:16:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷文就是綾香?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這...這到底是怎麼回事啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.47,0:16:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疾克!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.50,0:16:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.14,0:16:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼這麼傻\N妳為什麼會來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.78,0:16:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要死在這裡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.98,0:16:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我也要這樣子留下來\N不離開你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.05,0:16:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家明明都還很需要你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.72,0:16:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你卻想視而不見\N就這樣逃避...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.89,0:16:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所愛著的\N並不是這樣子的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.29,0:16:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.76,0:16:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼!\N桑德曼先生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.46,0:16:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸!\N桑德曼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.13,0:16:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.50,0:16:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我還留下了一些...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.14,0:16:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非完成不可的事情得去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.44,0:16:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷...雷文就是綾香?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.05,0:17:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧?真的嗎?為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.35,0:17:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個假面之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.86,0:17:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳承了自初代雷文開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.99,0:17:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代代雷文所保留下的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.83,0:17:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在戴著這面具的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.80,0:17:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就成為雷文的其中之一了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.24,0:17:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而這個假面呢...琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.91,0:17:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是從妳父親那裡繼承下來的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從我爸爸那裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.08,0:17:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此我的爸爸也曾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.72,0:17:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來...\N我一直都在綾香的身邊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.12,0:17:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N我一直都沒告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.36,0:17:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是當我戴著假面時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.82,0:17:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就非得扮演著雷文的角色才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你願意原諒姊姊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.60,0:17:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說我們是姊弟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.07,0:17:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.88,0:18:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去屬於我們的星球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.16,0:18:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位請注意這裡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.97,0:18:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豪魔開始...\N變成超巨型的大量殺戮機了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.90,0:18:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼還沒有結束啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.27,0:18:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是系統開始失控暴走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.62,0:18:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算用盡所有殘存能源\N朝著重力巨星和地球撞上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.65,0:18:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能源進入發射狀態\N迴避...來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.46,0:18:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底該怎麼辦才好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.33,0:18:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.83,0:18:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始進行最終合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.17,0:19:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最終合神?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.10,0:19:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.90,0:19:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烈陽超重神\N與神機Σ超重神合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.98,0:19:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神的最終進化型態!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.91,0:19:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙啟動工學型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.52,0:19:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.72,0:19:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.14,0:19:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最凶合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.68,0:19:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終極超重神!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.38,0:19:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓中央塔開始運作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.89,0:19:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把維持防護罩的能源\N全部釋放出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.46,0:19:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是超重戰艦.重力巨星\N最後的絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.36,0:19:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.06,0:20:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子能源...照射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.94,0:20:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子能源...完全填充!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.47,0:20:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迎戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.51,0:20:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.98,0:20:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.99,0:20:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重炎皇斬!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.57,0:20:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學終結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.95,0:20:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成...成...成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.89,0:20:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.42,0:21:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.02,0:21:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們打贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.46,0:21:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好強啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.83,0:21:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊強成這樣\N已經完全無法計算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們還真行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.03,0:21:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們果然好強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.51,0:21:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙桑德曼叔叔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.08,0:21:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的英司!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.18,0:21:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神棒透了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.55,0:21:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.49,0:21:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜您總統先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.99,0:21:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果到了最後\N還是須要仰賴他們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.36,0:21:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會的並不是這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.13,0:21:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是全面性的勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.06,0:21:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我們所有人類的勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.94,0:21:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你...我的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.28,0:21:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這宇宙中\N不論是什麼樣的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.65,0:22:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論是什麼人的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.82,0:22:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都美麗的閃爍著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.49,0:22:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年輕的生命啊茁壯成長吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.63,0:22:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且不管在任何地方\N都要如此的美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.37,0:22:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因熱戀而無法成眠的夜晚\N已經看膩了星座占卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.78,0:22:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為想要聽到人的聲音\N所以隨意打了電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.29,0:22:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了靠不住的語音留言\N你現在到底在哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.80,0:22:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,映著冰箱內的燈光\N我在狹小的宇宙裡彷徨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.74,0:23:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我的唱片\N唱針已經跳開不知幾次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.08,0:23:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我相信這不變的溫度\N一直到什麼時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.49,0:23:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OHBABY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.09,0:23:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.93,0:23:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們手牽著手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.77,0:23:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同被沁入你心中的\N淺淺呼吸籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.14,0:23:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳邊輕語嘛\N對讓我聽聽你溫柔的聲音嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.62,0:23:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們閉上雙眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.99,0:23:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一同在溜進你夢裡的\N甜美節奏中融化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.07,0:24:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綾香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.15,0:24:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好美...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.82,0:24:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳比這宇宙中的一切事物\N都還要更美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.59,0:24:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的綾香...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.73,0:25:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜恭喜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.10,0:25:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳了姊姊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.37,0:25:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.60,0:25:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你啊疾克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.11,0:25:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你費茲傑羅總統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.01,0:25:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和綾香姊姊\N看起來都好幸福的樣子喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:21.35,0:25:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子的夢想\N果然還是穿上新娘禮服啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:26.15,0:25:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那琉菜小姐的對象\N難道是英司少爺嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:29.16,0:25:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...不要胡扯了!\N為什麼我要和英司那種傢伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:33.43,0:25:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.90,0:25:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...那應該是我要說的話吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.93,0:25:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美的花束喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:40.13,0:25:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫做新娘捧花喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:42.04,0:25:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從新娘子手中接到捧花的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:43.94,0:25:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說將會是下一個結婚的人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:47.94,0:25:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接好囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.71,0:25:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捧花我要囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.51,0:25:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們想都別想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.35,0:25:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搶這個我可不能輸給妳們喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:56.95,0:25:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:58.12,0:26:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也希望自己能得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:00.92,0:26:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要定了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:02.82,0:26:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機會來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:04.13,0:26:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們別想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:04.96,0:26:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:06.83,0:26:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好運~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:07.80,0:26:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳休想!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:17.84,0:26:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司要和我結婚嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:20.84,0:26:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...你在胡說什麼啊?斗牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:22.88,0:26:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:23.48,0:26:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結婚是要一個男人和一個女人\N才能結的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:27.01,0:26:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:28.08,0:26:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊但是也有一些國家\N是可以讓兩個男人結婚的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.49,0:26:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在問題不是那個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:34.79,0:26:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行斗牙!\N你千萬別和英司和我好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:42.13,0:26:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美...